In Game of Thrones, there was a draconian civilization, they were called the Valyrians.  They had a slave economy enforced with the power of dragons.  The civilization died when their miners dug too deep, and unleashed an apocalypse of magma on their motherland.

Draconia will not make the same mistake.  We will mine the asteroids, not the planets.  Draconia will be rich beyond imagining.  And we will spread our way of life out to the stars.
